```{r}
library(tidyverse)
```



```{r}
Original_Data <- read.csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/apierre15/Final-Data-Science/main/HSE_Data.csv?token=AUX6FGZCDFGFVDUNBZFSND3BBGYNC")
Original_Data
```
# Create Sodium Data Table
```{r}
Sodium_Data <- Original_Data %>%
select(Sodium,Sodium.missing.flag)
Sodium_Data
```

# Create a histogram for all Sodium data points
```{r}
Sodium_Data %>%
  ggplot(Data = Sodium_Data) +
  geom_histogram()
```
